{"title":"雷锋","authors":["向求纬"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向求纬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁都见过那张照片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个军人　圆脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终微笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦拭方向盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住：是擦拭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是转动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦拭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反反复复的积累"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种甘于寂寞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素质的磨炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他也有一个响亮的姓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个削铁如泥的名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满可以盼望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次惊天动地的振响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次酣畅淋漓的亮相"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而　军装告诉他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原野更需要平凡的绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帽徽告诉他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜空更需要普通的星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对许多人　这是一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻而易举的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就算是两万多天吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两万多个最低标准"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开给生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两万多个最高标准"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开给工作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么　你便拥有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两万多个　有滋有味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不常提到工作了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作　是一座围城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进的　欲进难进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出的　似出非出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那位圆脸的兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用圆满的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将工作　擦拭成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种　雷锋式的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦拭　将人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打磨成人"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}